Climax Series C801 Keyless Locking Devices deliver a mechanical interference fit and provides a higher torque capacity over alternative keyed connections.

Climax Series C801 Features:
  • Single nut design allows for quick and simple installation
  • Lower contact pressure
  • Limited axial movement of mounted component during installation
  • Zinc plated rings with corrosion resistant nut
  • Imperial shaft sizes 5/8" to 3" and metric sizes 15mm to 75mm
  • Shaft and bore tolerance on all sizes: ±.003
  • Available from stock in Mentor, Ohio

  • Zinc plated rings with corrosion resistant nut

  • Shaft and bore tolerance on all sizes: ±.003
